# Vue Doctor Health Check (Vue-only)

When asked to run Vue Doctor, Vue health check, or Vue code analysis, follow the instructions in:
`.claude/skills/vue-doctor/SKILL.md`

## Quick Reference

**Usage:** Run on any Vue 3 project to get a 0-100 health score.
- `full` — full scan (default)
- `diff [base]` — diff-only scan against base branch
- `fix` — auto-fix safe issues (oxlint + eslint only; vue-tsc has no fix)

**Vue-only:** Automatically skips React-only projects.

**3-tool pipeline:** Oxlint + eslint-plugin-vue + vue-tsc (missing tools are skipped, not blockers).

**BANNED:**
- Running on React-only projects
- Fabricating diagnostics

For full protocol: read `.claude/skills/vue-doctor/SKILL.md`
